    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143630/extras/9222d7ad0e784001607ec218180767ad.avif?t=1729874876\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143630/extras_big/9222d7ad0e784001607ec218180767ad.avif?t=1729874876 width=800 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>准备好戴上你的工作帽吧！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你扮演的是疲惫不堪的工人，试图逃离致命工厂的恶性循环，那里没有简单的出路。传说中，只有一位伟大而神秘的人物成功逃脱。和4-8名玩家组队，享受纯粹的多人合作物理挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143630/extras/1f67e878b7efa8ab359f59553e6d1463.avif?t=1729874876\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143630/extras_big/1f67e878b7efa8ab359f59553e6d1463.avif?t=1729874876 width=800 height=41 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >享受合作物理挑战的乐趣</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143630/extras/eab2bba2f8ba5b8640a9f56d815a8685.poster.avif?t=1729874876\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143630/extras/eab2bba2f8ba5b8640a9f56d815a8685.webm?t=1729874876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143630/extras/eab2bba2f8ba5b8640a9f56d815a8685.mp4?t=1729874876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >体验动态的逃脱动作</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143630/extras/c1409d1e8af56fba031ae8dc070895f2.poster.avif?t=1729874876\" width=800 height=448 